    - Fixed Eric's email address.
    - Added BabyURL.com
    - Added URLjr.com

---
version: 1.85
date:    30 Aug 2003
changes:
    - Added v3.net
    - Assorted documentation tidyups.

---
version: 1.84
date:    29 Aug 2003
changes:
    - Changed URL for shorlfilter.
    - Fixed qURL documentation.
    - Added tinylink.com
    - SmLnk.pm now uses the SmLnk API.

---
version: 1.83
date:    26 Aug 2003
